parameters.query:
select u.id
, u.uuid
, concat(u.first_name, ' ', u.last_name) as host_name
, u.email 
, count(distinct case when b.status = 'completed' then b.id end) as completed_bookings
, min(CASE WHEN b.status = 'completed' THEN b.request_end_at END) as request_end
from listings l 
left join bookings b on b.listing_id = l.id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = l.id 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id 
where 1=1 
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
--and l.id = '20035'
group by 1,2,3 
having count(distinct case when b.status = 'completed' then b.id end) = 1
and min(CASE WHEN b.status = 'completed' THEN b.request_end_at END)::DATE = NOW()::DATE
